{"id":"6459223dd13353a0f97e6d46","title":"Archivebox で UA 変更","image":null,"created":1683563069,"updated":1683563078,"lines":[{"id":"6459223dd13353a0f97e6d46","text":"Archivebox で UA 変更","created":1683563069,"updated":1683563069},{"id":"6459223d4ade4d0000e56848","text":"from [20230507] #0507","created":1683563069,"updated":1683563074},{"id":"6459223d4ade4d0000e56849","text":"[Archivebox] で [UA] 変更","created":1683563069,"updated":1683563069},{"id":"6459223d4ade4d0000e5684a","text":"\tURL を追加した際に [403] ではね返されることがあった","created":1683563069,"updated":1683563078},{"id":"6459223d4ade4d0000e5684b","text":"\t\tUA で弾く系のサイトで起きてるみたい","created":1683563069,"updated":1683563069},{"id":"6459223d4ade4d0000e5684c","text":"\t\thttps://docs.archivebox.io/en/v0.6.2/Configuration.html","created":1683563069,"updated":1683563069},{"id":"6459223d4ade4d0000e5684d","text":"\t\tをみると、conf を書き換えればいいようだが、web の UI に設定が反映されていないようにみえる","created":1683563069,"updated":1683563069},{"id":"6459223d4ade4d0000e5684e","text":"\t\t設定を書き換えて [CLI] の方では設定が反映されてたので web のサーバを再起動すればいいのかーと","created":1683563069,"updated":1683563069},{"id":"6459223d4ade4d0000e5684f","text":"\t\tただ、`archivebox server` に restart とか reload 的なサブコマンドがなくて、とりあえず process を kill した","created":1683563069,"updated":1683563069},{"id":"6459223d4ade4d0000e56850","text":"\t\tで、過去にも `archivebox server` でサーバをあげてたようだが、フォアグラウンドでサーバが立ち上がってしまってシェルが抜けられなかった","created":1683563069,"updated":1683563069},{"id":"6459223d4ade4d0000e56851","text":"\t\t起動しっぱなしにする方法がわからなかったので `systemctl` の service を書いてしのいだ...","created":1683563069,"updated":1683563069},{"id":"6459223d4ade4d0000e56852","text":"","created":1683563069,"updated":1683563069}]}